{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was an experience that I find very difficult to describe, that human beings exist who are capable of doing things, what this man did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He-- he got pleasure out of killing people, the Jews, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he always-- it was more of a challenge to him to pick the big and the tall ones.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there wasn't a day that I remember that he wasn't drunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to get out in the middle of the night and to stand on the Appellplatz, which was the center of the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had to-- in the wintertime, I remember we had to stand naked there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to crawl in the snow, and the winters are severe there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Most of the time, he did this-- what he called gymnastics after you came in from a day's work, from 10, 12 hours in the factory.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The camp itself-- we are-- we had about 2,000 in these little labor camps, and they were just barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Didn't get a chance to wash yourself, or we didn't have any underwear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There weren't any showers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you're lucky, there was a faucet, and if you had a chance to use the faucet to wash yourself off a little bit-- looking back, I-- I never had any underwear when we were there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Food was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Sleeping quarters-- we had a barrack, and there were three-tier wooden shelves like, and that's where you lied on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when you woke up in the morning, and you looked around, and there were always one or so that didn't make the night, and you wondered, maybe they're better off than you are.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
